== Remarks ==
[[SDL_JoyAxisEvent]] is a member of the [[SDL_Event]] structure and is used when an event of type SDL_JOYAXISMOTION is reported.

A SDL_JOYAXISMOTION event occurs whenever a user moves an axis on the joystick.

